        "created_at": "2022-08-09T01:42:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I think 1991 is a highly overlooked vintage.  Might be asking a lot for a Santenay to go 31 years, but it wouldn\u2019t surprise me.  Charles Noellat was bought by Leroy some time ago.</p>",
