        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"284706\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I think 1991 is a highly overlooked vintage.  Might be asking a lot for a Santenay to go 31 years, but it wouldn\u2019t surprise me.  Charles Noellat was bought by Leroy some time ago.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>bought in 88 but I believe some wines and vineyards were not included in the sale.</p>",
