        "id": 3863662,
        "name": "Mark C Johnson",
        "username": "Mark_C_Johnson",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/mark_c_johnson/{size}/866_2.png",
        "created_at": "2022-08-09T06:55:59.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve purchased some of these older Charles Noellat wines.  Not earth shattering but if you let stand to settle the sediment and \u201caudouze\u201d for an hour or so, they show respectably well.  I would start with the village and see how that goes, then do the 1er if that isn\u2019t painfully obvious.</p>\n<p>Goodluck.</p>",
